  <li>Maharashtra</li>
  <li>Orissa</li>
  <li>Bhuj</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Ans :-</strong> Bhuj</p>

<p><strong>Question 5 :</strong> Where did the Banarasi weave originate from?</p>

